    "content": "# 1. 리포지토리\n\n\n[link_preview](https://github.com/ryoon-with-wisdomtrees/RyoonThread)\n\n\n# 2. 사이트\n\n\n<BookMarkWrapper names={\"bookmark\"} urls={\"https://thread-inspired-clone-with-ryoon.vercel.app/sign-in\"} />\n\n\n# 3. RyoonThread\n\n\n![Untitled.gif](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/056ff9f5-a9ef-486f-8acb-9eef51d06a2d/0baf21a5-4108-40f7-8e9e-f7bd138336b2/Untitled.gif?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466QBD62PLT%2F20250808%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20250808T053922Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEGUaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIEDxhxTJqSpObo7HZE80%2FdEzcc7Lp7nyT41SofmeKvluAiAQNcpDfh2zHXuxtJUzB9naZhmdsg6ihQ3gdXhV7jQeoyqIBAie%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIMmyf63oZThebtYM5jKtwDw6NCguEfnmBAfIh3smN0txYPwxz6W2lb00C8PzkDD8vBybjjleqSdyNbZzC1kkRLqhqaYW%2B5YDtG05e275RkoqpqkwUlFOYL0J68OyvQ%2Bcf0PFm4Oo%2Fr9IWEJxYVVuBLaf51XrhDqEHCemgGZjWo9bbeTzMnGOGdQJgoqRemSPT4OR5ZinkyfS%2BWInu4BxyhncWhCkgyKHoXknI62DHNJcbO8AjE5%2BC463trRyDWwlvZzDS5%2FRhqwVwTAWVqG9L%2FxEQcNmm2HpUSOucPAS1e58gOFb0mestqOIf3TX2qvhkVuW2Jzaj485b4yCxv17B6n6Yuub7vmDwadoB9SoZAX9LAP1VIwonko0XjFxrOqaRtTFNp4qtDKiPMwykHQvhU4k6BSWlHXrfYXgALUsl%2BL%2BUYhW52E3r17%2FiUwCl7omFAIFgoFyzuaUd6RzZhiwfyw%2Ff11DbCAZXpNsdOGDga1UXFHAy%2F%2FXSPxAr8OSb02yaLEpbPeS0oBvC75ytLyAsbHlZExleLCyO%2FpaOm044R%2BXa3xzTKatYQbiOvgR%2FvgCWYiN29qTS3nZLO1X%2Fu%2BDYh6qckmmPxopg5%2B96EBObQ0SF0LcuLduuX7wfITG7GKmCVp1%2FcqiVPicFhAqIwuoTWxAY6pgFAdGWDt0vweaCkzrp1anX5%2B8gpTY36JrdwdV0LLfCnUihsM%2Fqp40%2BteDLGRvoMmbfYiY0kJuKjl2tpimcWjK2QtGSK3%2B%2BUR%2BXuLQiaCqvD66EHVfRBzM3rTr4B7%2FSvjcBO64C3%2FsKbG3l%2BnHrZmewTlYKg82iGg5VJme0HW7NY1DiVxVR0eBVtKmPanfc3E5mYyJ2xB24rjJwsz8sNg41x0FU4As1K&X-Amz-Signature=936626cd79c32359f6ca3d1cebf8c6292b1d7cc334904b6578e7c19aa0aaec20&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject)\n\n- RyoonThread(Thread-Clone ver.2) is a full Stack MERN Next.js 14 Threads App with React, TypeScript, MongoDB, uploadingthing, zod etc..\n- 기존의 [Thread clone app](https://threads-ryoon.vercel.app/)에서 추가적으로 기능구현하여 작성한 Thread ver.2 WEB-APP입니다.\n\n## 4. 추가 적용한 작업 및 기능( 2023.11 기준)\n\n- 현재 사용되는 Thread app과 가장 유사한 레이아웃으로 구성되도록 변경하였습니다.\n- 스레드 작성 컴포넌트도, Page로 이동하는 방식에서 Modal컴포넌트로 뜨도록 변경하였습니다.\n- 다국어 기능을 적용 하였습니다.\n- Darkmode를 적용 하였습니다.\n- Search, Delete, Block 등의 기능을 추가적으로 적용하였습니다.\n\n## 5. 그 외에 배우고 적용한 것\n\n\nWith This Project, I've learned:\n\n- Next.js 13.4 with Server Side Rendering\n- Learned MongoDB handling of complex schemas, multiple data population\n- Created beautiful layouts with TailwindCSS\n- Used Clerk for authentication\n- Handled file uploads with UploadThing\n- Explored Shadcn components\n- Listend to real-time events with webhooks\n- Understood middleware, API actions, and authorization\n- Explored & integrate new Next.js layout route groups\n- Validated data with Zod\n- Managed forms with react hook form\n- Created reusable components\n- Built a solid application architecture\n- Deployed the application with Vercel",
